WEBVTT

00:01.601 --> 00:04.235
All: [Chanting]
Off our land! Off our land!

00:04.260 --> 00:05.595
[Truck horn honking]

00:05.620 --> 00:08.455
Off our land! Off our land!

00:08.480 --> 00:12.465
- Off our land! Off our land!
- Man: You'll destroy what is not yours!

00:13.627 --> 00:15.446
The blasts always get them riled up.

00:15.471 --> 00:18.090
Yeah, tell them it's the sound of progress!

00:18.115 --> 00:21.619
♪

00:23.489 --> 00:25.180
Good morning, Boss!

00:25.205 --> 00:26.949
What the hell's so good about it?!

00:26.973 --> 00:29.643
Pace we're going, we ain't never
gonna get that damn pond drained!

00:29.668 --> 00:31.668
Well, we're still waiting
on that last permit, Isaac.

00:31.693 --> 00:32.706
Protesters slowing everything down.

00:32.731 --> 00:34.559
We got this job based on our reputation

00:34.584 --> 00:37.319
- for being fast... real fast.
- It's Oklahoma.

00:37.344 --> 00:38.847
You know better than anyone how the locals

00:38.873 --> 00:42.039
- feel about their tribal lands and whatnot.
- Yeah, I do.

00:42.064 --> 00:44.398
Never should've given those
people anything anyway.

00:44.423 --> 00:46.173
Now, look, I want you to
lay this last section,

00:46.198 --> 00:47.978
get that damn pond drained
and finish this job,

00:48.003 --> 00:50.522
otherwise, those gassers are gonna
be looking for a whole new crew.

00:50.547 --> 00:53.214
- Soon as that last permit comes in, we'll be...
- I got the permit.

00:53.239 --> 00:54.572
Well, records say it ain't on file.

00:54.597 --> 00:56.765
Well, if I say I got it, Andy, I got it.

00:57.728 --> 01:00.062
You just go on and do your job, will you?

01:00.087 --> 01:01.759
You're the boss.

01:01.784 --> 01:05.285
♪

01:12.168 --> 01:14.663
[Rumbling, cracking]

01:16.075 --> 01:18.275
[Grunts]

01:18.300 --> 01:20.473
Aah!

01:20.498 --> 01:22.164
Andy?!

01:22.632 --> 01:24.488
Hang on! We're coming for you!

01:24.513 --> 01:26.354
Rope and ladder! Go get rope and ladder!

01:26.379 --> 01:28.663
[Groans]

01:28.688 --> 01:30.721
[Indistinct shouting in distance]

01:30.746 --> 01:33.207
[Sighs]

01:33.232 --> 01:36.077
[Grunts]

01:40.656 --> 01:43.323
[Wind whistling]

01:46.149 --> 01:48.611
Isaac: Hold on there, Andy!

01:54.225 --> 01:56.313
- [Coughs]
- Get ahold of that, Andy!

01:56.338 --> 01:58.255
Come on, get him up there.

01:58.307 --> 01:59.639
[Grunting]

01:59.675 --> 02:01.558
[Grunts]

02:01.593 --> 02:04.488
- [Grunts]
- [Coughing]

02:04.513 --> 02:06.263
- You all right?
- Oh, yeah.

02:06.315 --> 02:08.315
Yeah, I think I just hit my head.

02:08.350 --> 02:10.567
All right, sit him down over
there, get him some water.

02:10.602 --> 02:11.852
Come on.

02:14.606 --> 02:17.858
♪

02:26.134 --> 02:31.134
- Synced and corrected by martythecrazy -
<b><font color="#008000">WEB-DL resync by</font> kinglouisxx</b>
